Two of Schneider's best comedies for the price of one. Each movie is on a separate disc. A good deal overall.
Bought this combo pack for Deuce Bigalow and the Hot Chick was a bonus!  Love seeing Rob Schneider in both these roles!
My Daughter loves both of these movies and is watching them a lot. She has no cable, so movies help.
Absolutely love Deuce Biggelow, to get the Hot Chick thrown in was a bonus.  Great no-brains humor.  Not for kids.

My niece was wanting to borrow my copy of the HOT CHICK which I couldn't find. I bought this to  surprize  her.  She  loved it. She took it on the Father's Day family vacation. They hadn't seen Deuce and they thought it was funny.
Love these under $5 movies; good to add to the collection; this one came well packaged and the delivery was quick, the movies themselves are stupid and funny; I do recommend !

These are two of my all-time favorite movies!! Both are hilarious! I don't even remember the last time I bought a DVD since practically everything is available on Netflix or Hulu, but I couldn't pass up these classics for the price!
They are both greatly funny films. I loved HOT CHICK, it is so funny! :) It is so funny! ANNA FARIS is a great actress! :)
Funny Movies if all time I love my purchase. AND THE DVD PLAYS WONDERFUL
